text: Kryptos koehleri is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Buccinidae, the true whelks. ==Description== The length of the shell varies between 10 mm and 20 mm. ==Distribution== This species occurs in the North Atlantic Ocean (Bay of Biscay, Morocco, Azores) ==References== * Bouchet P. & Warén A. (1985). Revision of the Northeast Atlantic bathyal and abyssal Neogastropoda excluding Turridae (Mollusca, Gastropoda). Bollettino Malacologico Suppl. 1: 121–296 ==External links== * Category:Buccinidae Category:Gastropods described in 1896
title: Kryptos koehleri
